<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="Holding familiar focada em Venture Capital, Private Equity e Blockchain. Conectamos capital a empreendedores visionários para gerar liberdade financeira." />
    <meta name="keywords" content="Venture Capital, Private Equity, Investimentos, Blockchain, Startups, Holding Familiar, Liberdade Financeira, Tokenização" />
    <title>Golden Investimentos | Venture Capital & Private Equity</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: "Manrope", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #F0F0F0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 2rem;
            }
        }

        /* Navigation */
        header {
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 50;
            background-color: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #D4AF37;
            height: 80px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header .container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 48px;
            width: auto;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .logo img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        nav ul {
            display: none;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                display: flex;
            }
        }

        nav a {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -4px;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover::after,
        nav a.active::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .menu-toggle {
            display: block;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .menu-toggle {
                display: none;
            }
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 90vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #D4AF37;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1) 0%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9) 100%);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .hero .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 4rem;
            }
        }

        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
            background-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            color: #D4AF37;
            font-family: "Space Grotesk", monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .hero-badge::before {
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
        }

        .hero h1 .gold {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #D4AF37, #F0E6C8, #D4AF37);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #D1D5DB;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            border-left: 2px solid #D4AF37;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .button-group {
                flex-direction: row;
            }
        }

        button, a.btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 0;
            font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #050505;
            border-color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border-color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: #050505;
        }

        .hero-image {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            animation: slideInRight 0.7s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .hero-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 500px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 50px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3));
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .hero-image img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Sections */
        section {
            padding: 5rem 0;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            section h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
        }

        section h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Portfolio Section */
        .portfolio {
            background-color: #000000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333333;
        }

        .portfolio-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .portfolio-header p {
            color: #9CA3AF;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            font-family: "Space Grotesk", monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .portfolio-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .portfolio-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .portfolio-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            }
        }

        .portfolio-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: transparent;
            border: none;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            min-height: 150px;
        }

        .portfolio-item:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .portfolio-item img {
            max-width: 100%;
            max-height: 100px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            background-color: #F9F5E8;
            color: #050505;
        }

        .features-header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            md:flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .features h2 {
            color: #050505;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
        }

        .feature-card {
            padding: 2.5rem;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .feature-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 96px;
            height: 96px;
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            border-radius: 0 0 0 100%;
            margin-right: -48px;
            margin-top: -48px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            border-color: #D4AF37;
            box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px 0px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-card:hover::before {
            background-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #D4AF37;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: #666666;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            border-top: 4px solid #D4AF37;
        }

        .about-header {
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 6rem 0;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-header .gold {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .about-header p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #D1D5DB;
            border-left: 4px solid #D4AF37;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 48rem;
        }

        .about-content {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: #050505;
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .about-content .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .about-content .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .about-content h2 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .about-content p {
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .about-checklist {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .about-checklist {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .checklist-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #050505;
        }

        .checklist-item::before {
            content: '✓';
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #050505;
            font-weight: 800;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .about-image {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .about-image::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -16px;
            left: -16px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: 2px solid #D4AF37;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .about-image-inner {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #050505;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 400px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3));
        }

        .about-values {
            background-color: #F9F5E8;
            padding: 6rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .about-values h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-values-intro {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            max-width: 48rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .values-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .values-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
        }

        .value-card {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover {
            border-color: #D4AF37;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .value-icon {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .value-card:hover .value-icon {
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #050505;
        }

        .value-card h3 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .value-card p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Services Section */
        .services {
            background-color: #F9F5E8;
            color: #050505;
        }

        .services-header {
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #D4AF37;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .services-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .services-header .gold {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .services-header p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            max-width: 42rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .services-list {
            padding: 6rem 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6rem;
        }

        .service-item {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .service-item {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }

            .service-item.reverse {
                direction: rtl;
            }

            .service-item.reverse > * {
                direction: ltr;
            }
        }

        .service-content h2 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .service-content p {
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .service-features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .service-features {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .service-feature {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            color: #050505;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .service-feature::before {
            content: '';
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .service-image {
            position: relative;
        }

        .service-image::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            transform: translate(16px, 16px);
            border: 2px solid #050505;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .service-image-inner {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            border: 2px solid #050505;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        .service-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
            transition: filter 0.5s ease;
        }

        .service-item:hover .service-image img {
            filter: grayscale(0%);
        }

        .services-investors {
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .services-investors h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .services-investors-intro {
            text-align: center;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .investors-divider {
            width: 96px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            margin: 0 auto 4rem;
        }

        .investors-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .investors-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }
        }

        .investor-card {
            background-color: #121212;
            padding: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid #333333;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .investor-card:hover {
            border-color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .investor-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .investor-card h3 {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .investor-card p {
            color: #9CA3AF;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Coins Section */
        .coins {
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            border-top: 4px solid #D4AF37;
        }

        .coins-split {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 0;
            min-height: 90vh;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .coins-split {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .coin-side {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333333;
            transition: background-color 0.5s ease;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .coin-side {
                border-bottom: none;
                border-right: 1px solid #333333;
                padding: 5rem;
            }

            .coin-side:last-child {
                border-right: none;
            }
        }

        .coin-side:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        }

        .coin-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            padding: 0.375rem 0.75rem;
            border: 1px solid #D4AF37;
            color: #D4AF37;
            font-family: "Space Grotesk", monospace;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            width: fit-content;
        }

        .coin-badge.green {
            border-color: #22C55E;
            color: #22C55E;
        }

        .coin-title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .coin-title .highlight {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .coin-title .highlight.green {
            color: #22C55E;
        }

        .coin-description {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: #D1D5DB;
            line-height: 1.8;
            max-width: 28rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .coin-image-small {
            width: 192px;
            height: 192px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .coin-image-small img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3));
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .coin-side:hover .coin-image-small img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .coin-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            width: fit-content;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .coin-buttons {
                flex-direction: row;
            }
        }

        /* Coin Benefits */
        .coin-benefits {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: #050505;
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .coin-benefits h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .coin-benefits-intro {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
            max-width: 48rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .benefits-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .benefits-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 3rem;
            }
        }

        .benefits-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .benefit-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .benefit-item:hover {
            border-color: #D4AF37;
            background-color: #F9F5E8;
        }

        .benefit-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #D4AF37;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .benefit-content h3 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
        }

        .benefit-content p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .wallet-box {
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 3rem;
            border: 4px solid #D4AF37;
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 400px;
        }

        .wallet-box h3 {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .wallet-box p {
            color: #9CA3AF;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact {
            background-color: #0A0A0A;
            border-top: 4px solid #D4AF37;
        }

        .contact-header {
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 5rem 0;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #D4AF37;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-header .gold {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .contact-header p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            max-width: 42rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .contact-content {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: #050505;
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }

        .contact-content .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            .contact-content .container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .contact-info h2 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .contact-channels {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .contact-channel {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-channel-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
            color: #D4AF37;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .contact-channel-content h3 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-channel-content p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .contact-form {
            background-color: #F9F5E8;
            padding: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
        }

        .contact-form h3 {
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #9CA3AF;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        input, textarea, select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            color: #050505;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 0;
        }

        input::placeholder, textarea::placeholder {
            color: #D1D5DB;
        }

        input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #D4AF37;
        }

        textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        /* CTA Section */
        .cta {
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #050505;
            padding: 6rem 0;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cta h2 {
            color: #050505;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .cta h2 {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }
        }

        .cta p {
            text-align: center;
            color: #050505;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            max-width: 42rem;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: row;
            }
        }

        .cta .btn-primary {
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border-color: #050505;
        }

        .cta .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            color: #050505;
        }

        .cta .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: #050505;
            border-color: #050505;
        }

        .cta .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: #050505;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #050505;
            border-top: 1px solid #333333;
            padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
            color: #9CA3AF;
        }

        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .footer-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            }
        }

        footer h4 {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        footer ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        footer li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #9CA3AF;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #D4AF37;
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid #333333;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .footer-bottom {
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }

        /* Utilities */
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .mb-4 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .mb-8 {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .mt-4 {
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .w-full {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .hidden {
            display: none;
        }

        .scroll-indicator {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 1rem;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 20;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(10px); }
        }

        .scroll-indicator span {
            font-size: 0.625rem;
            font-family: "Space Grotesk", monospace;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .scroll-indicator-line {
            width: 1px;
            height: 48px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0));
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header/Navigation -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo" onclick="scrollToSection('inicio')">
                <img src="images/logo_black.png" alt="Golden Investimentos" />
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#inicio" class="nav-link">INÍCIO</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#portfolio" class="nav-link">PORTFOLIO</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#sobre" class="nav-link">SOBRE</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#servicos" class="nav-link">SERVIÇOS</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#moeda" class="nav-link">MOEDA GOLDEN</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contato" class="nav-link">CONTATO</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
            <button class="menu-toggle">☰</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero" id="inicio">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="hero-badge">
                    Venture Capital & Private Equity
                </div>
                <h1>SUSTENTABILIDADE,<br><span class="gold">CIRCULARIDADE E LIBERDADE FINANCEIRA</span></h1>
                <p>A Golden Investimentos é uma holding familiar (family office) financeira e não financeira que conecta capital a empreendedores visionários, startups e empreendimentos de alto impacto. Transformamos ideias inovadoras em líderes de mercado dispostos a ser, fazer e ter sustentabilidade e liberdade financeira.</p>
                <div class="button-group">
                    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="scrollToSection('contato')">Buscar Investimento</button>
                    <button class="btn-outline" onclick="scrollToSection('portfolio')">Conhecer Portfolio</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="images/moeda_v2.png" alt="Golden Coin" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator" onclick="scrollToSection('portfolio')">
            <span>Role para baixo</span>
            <div class="scroll-indicator-line"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Portfolio Section -->
    <section class="portfolio" id="portfolio">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="portfolio-header">
                <p>Nosso Ecossistema</p>
                <h2>EMPRESAS DO PORTFOLIO</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-grid">
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-1.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-3.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-5.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-7.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-9.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-11.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-13.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-15.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-17.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-19.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-21.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
                <div class="portfolio-item"><img src="images/partners_white/logo-23.png" alt="Partner" /></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="features-header">
                <div>
                    <h2>INVESTIMOS EM<br><span style="color: #D4AF37;">QUEM FAZ ACONTECER</span></h2>
                    <p style="color: #666666; font-size: 1.125rem; margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 32rem;">Não somos apenas investidores. Somos parceiros estratégicos que aportam capital, conhecimento e networking para escalar negócios disruptivos.</p>
                </div>
                <button class="btn-outline" style="background-color: #050505; color: #FFFFFF; border-color: #050505;" onclick="scrollToSection('sobre')">Nossa Tese de Investimento →</button>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">💡</div>
                    <h3>Inovação Disruptiva</h3>
                    <p>Buscamos startups que estão redefinindo mercados e criando novas categorias de consumo e serviço.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                    <h3>Empreendedorismo</h3>
                    <p>Além do capital, oferecemos mentoria, acesso a mercados e suporte operacional para o crescimento.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🌍</div>
                    <h3>Escalabilidade Global</h3>
                    <p>Focamos em modelos de negócio com potencial de expansão internacional e crescimento exponencial.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about" id="sobre">
        <div class="about-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>NOSSA <span class="gold">MISSÃO</span></h1>
                <p>A Golden Investimentos nasceu para ser o combustível de negócios extraordinários. Somos uma firma de Venture Capital dedicada a identificar, investir e escalar as startups que definirão o futuro.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="container">
                <div>
                    <h2>MAIS QUE CAPITAL, PARCERIA ESTRATÉGICA</h2>
                    <p>Golden Investimentos entende que o êxito de uma empresa é sua comunidade empreendedora resiliente e líderes com capacidade de interdependência colaborativa que gerenciam riscos com o fim de cumprir com uma demanda do mercado oferecendo produtos e serviços de excelência para gerar investimento de valor.</p>
                    <p>Atuamos em Agricultura irrigada, programas genéticos, energias renováveis, Fintech e Blockchain as service, incorporação imobiliária, domótica IoT, inteligência artificial, acreditação de carbono e Cleantechs, bem-estar e telemedicina.</p>
                    <p>Fundada por Julio Camargo Majfud e Jimena Mercadal. Golden Investimentos é a holding financeira e não financeira familiar Camargo Mercadal Investimentos Ltda.</p>
                    <div class="about-checklist">
                        <div class="checklist-item">Dinheiro inteligente</div>
                        <div class="checklist-item">Acesso a mentores</div>
                        <div class="checklist-item">Redes globais</div>
                        <div class="checklist-item">Suporte Operacional</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <div class="about-image-inner">
                        <img src="images/moeda_v2.png" alt="Golden Coin" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-values">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>NOSSOS PILARES</h2>
                <p class="about-values-intro">Investimos em pessoas e ideias que têm o poder de transformar mercados.</p>
                <div class="values-grid">
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon">🚀</div>
                        <h3>Inovação</h3>
                        <p>Buscamos soluções disruptivas que resolvam problemas reais de forma escalável.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon">💼</div>
                        <h3>Empreendedorismo</h3>
                        <p>Apoiamos fundadores resilientes e visionários, que não têm medo de desafiar o status quo.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="value-card">
                        <div class="value-icon">👥</div>
                        <h3>Colaboração</h3>
                        <p>Acreditamos na força do ecossistema e na troca de conhecimento entre nossas investidas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section class="services" id="servicos">
        <div class="services-header">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>O QUE <span class="gold">OFERECEMOS</span></h1>
                <p>Soluções completas para impulsionar o crescimento de startups e conectar investidores a oportunidades únicas.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="services-list">
                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 80px; height: 80px; background-color: #D4AF37; color: #050505; border: 2px solid #050505; box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 0px rgba(0,0,0,1); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 2rem;">🚀</div>
                        <h2>Venture Capital</h2>
                        <p>Investimento em startups de alto potencial de crescimento, do Seed ao Series A.</p>
                        <div class="service-features">
                            <div class="service-feature">Aporte de capital</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Mentoria estratégica</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Acesso a networking</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Suporte em captação futura</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">M&A</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Estruturação de finanças descentralizadas</div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn-primary" style="background-color: #050505; color: #FFFFFF; border-color: #050505;">Saiba Mais</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-image">
                        <div class="service-image-inner">
                            <img src="images/service_vc_coin_6f6e4be0.png" alt="Venture Capital" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item reverse">
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 80px; height: 80px; background-color: #D4AF37; color: #050505; border: 2px solid #050505; box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 0px rgba(0,0,0,1); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 2rem;">📈</div>
                        <h2>Aceleração de Negócios</h2>
                        <p>Programas intensivos para estruturar e escalar seu negócio em tempo recorde.</p>
                        <div class="service-features">
                            <div class="service-feature">Validação de modelo de negócio</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Growth hacking</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Estruturação financeira</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Preparação para exit</div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn-primary" style="background-color: #050505; color: #FFFFFF; border-color: #050505;">Saiba Mais</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-image">
                        <div class="service-image-inner">
                            <img src="images/service_acceleration_coin_bbe73b95.png" alt="Aceleração" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="service-item">
                    <div class="service-content">
                        <div style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 80px; height: 80px; background-color: #D4AF37; color: #050505; border: 2px solid #050505; box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 0px rgba(0,0,0,1); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 2rem;">🏢</div>
                        <h2>Corporate Venture</h2>
                        <p>Conectamos grandes empresas a startups inovadoras para gerar valor mútuo.</p>
                        <div class="service-features">
                            <div class="service-feature">Open innovation</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">M&A estratégico</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Parcerias comerciais</div>
                            <div class="service-feature">Transformação digital</div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn-primary" style="background-color: #050505; color: #FFFFFF; border-color: #050505;">Saiba Mais</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="service-image">
                        <div class="service-image-inner">
                            <img src="images/service_corporate_coin_0b799c56.png" alt="Corporate Venture" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="services-investors">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>PARA INVESTIDORES</h2>
                <div class="investors-divider"></div>
                <div class="investors-grid">
                    <div class="investor-card">
                        <div class="investor-icon">🛡️</div>
                        <h3>Curadoria Rigorosa</h3>
                        <p>Analisamos centenas de startups para selecionar apenas as melhores oportunidades de investimento.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="investor-card">
                        <div class="investor-icon">💰</div>
                        <h3>Tokenização de Ativos</h3>
                        <p>Acesso a investimentos em startups através da nossa moeda digital, garantindo liquidez e transparência.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="investor-card">
                        <div class="investor-icon">👥</div>
                        <h3>Clube de Investidores</h3>
                        <p>Faça parte de uma rede exclusiva de investidores anjo e venture capitalists.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Coins Section -->
    <section class="coins" id="moeda">
        <div class="coins-split">
            <div class="coin-side">
                <div class="coin-badge">Token Utilitário & Investimento</div>
                <h1 class="coin-title">GOLDEN <br><span class="highlight">NOTES</span></h1>
                <p class="coin-description">É um ativo digital com plataforma de tokenização de ativos e Smart contract.</p>
                <div class="coin-image-small">
                    <img src="images/moeda_v2.png" alt="Golden Notes" />
                </div>
                <div class="coin-buttons">
                    <a href="https://golden-notes.io/" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Comprar Tokens</a>
                    <a href="https://www.golden-notes.com/_files/ugd/1e54a2_c54d714e28524775885346578492e90b.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn-outline">Whitepaper</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="coin-side">
                <div class="coin-badge green">Infraestrutura & Tecnologia</div>
                <h1 class="coin-title">GOLDEN <br><span class="highlight green">BLOCKCHAIN</span></h1>
                <p class="coin-description">Tokenização de ativos digitais com smart contract e escrow account peer-to-peer pela liberdade financeira.</p>
                <div class="coin-image-small">
                    <img src="images/partners_white/logo-48.png" alt="Golden Blockchain" />
                </div>
                <div class="coin-buttons">
                    <button class="btn-primary">Conhecer Tecnologia</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="coin-benefits">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>POR QUE INVESTIR?</h2>
                <p class="coin-benefits-intro">Golden Blockchain é um ecossistema de tokenização de ativos através de um Smart Contract sobre a Blockchain Bitcoin. Permite ter securitização, trazabilidade e é o combustível de todo o ecossistema.</p>
                <div class="benefits-grid">
                    <div class="benefits-list">
